quran[856]{c,v,t}:
  26,1,T S M
  26,2,"Those are The Book`s, the clear/evident verses/evidences"
  26,3,Maybe/perhaps you (are) exhausting/destroying yourself from anger that they not be believing
  26,4,"If We want We descend on them from the sky an evidence/sign , so their necks continued/became to it bending/leaning"
  26,5,And none from a reminder initiated/originated from the merciful comes to them except they were from it objecting/opposing
  26,6,"So they had lied/denied/falsified so (the) news/information (of) what they were with it mocking/making fun of, will come to them"
  26,7,Do they not see to the earth/Planet Earth how many/much We sprouted/grew in it from every/each generous pair
  26,8,"That in that (is) an evidence/sign (E) , and most of them were not believing"
  26,9,"And that your Lord He is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"
  26,10,"And when Moses called/cried (to) your Lord that: \"Come/bring the nation the unjust/oppressive"
  26,11,"Pharaoh`s nation, do they not fear and obey"
  26,12,"He said: \"My Lord, that I, I fear that they deny me"
  26,13,"And my chest narrows/tightens and my tongue/speech does not speak/clarify, so send to Aaron"
  26,14,"And for them on (against) me (is) a crime, so I fear that they kill me"
  26,15,"He said: \"No but, so you (B) go/go away with Our verses/evidences/signs, that We are with you hearing/listening"
  26,16,"So you (B) come to Pharaoh, so say (B): `That we are messenger(s) (of) the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,17,That send with us Israel`s sons and daughters
  26,18,"He said: \"Did we not bring you up in (between) us (as) a child/new born, and you stayed/remained in (between) us years from your lifetime"
  26,19,"And you made/did your one deed/act which you made/did, and you are from the disbelievers"
  26,20,"He said: \"I made/did it then, and (while) I am from the misguided"
  26,21,"So I escaped/fled from you when I feared you, so my Lord granted for me judgment/rule, and He made/put me from the messengers"
  26,22,"And that is a blessing/goodness you brag/remind me repetitiously of , that you enslaved Israel`s sons and daughters"
  26,23,"Pharaoh said: \"And what (is) the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,24,"He (Moses) said: \"Lord (of) the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth, and what (is) between them (B), if youwere sure/certain"
  26,25,"He (Pharaoh) said to whom (was) around/surrounding him: \"Do you not hear/listen"
  26,26,"He (Moses) said: \"Your Lord, and your first/beginning father`s/forefather`s Lord"
  26,27,"He (Pharaoh) said: \"That your messenger who was sent to you (is) mad/insane (E)"
  26,28,"He (Moses) said: \"Lord (of) the sunrise/east and the sunset/west and what (is) between them (B) if you were reasoning/comprehending"
  26,29,"He (Pharaoh) said: \"If (E) you took/received a god other than me, I will make you (E) from the imprisoned/prisoners"
  26,30,"He (Moses) said: \"Even if I came to you with a clear/evident thing"
  26,31,"He (Pharaoh) said: \"So come/bring with it if you were from the truthful"
  26,32,"So he threw/threw away his stick/cane, so then it is (a) clear/evident snake"
  26,33,And he removed/pulled his hand so then it is white to the lookers/seers
  26,34,"He said to the nobles/assembly around/surrounding him, that, that (is) a knowledgeable magician/sorcerer (E)"
  26,35,"He wants/intends that he brings you out from your land with his magic/sorcery, so what (do) you order/command"
  26,36,"They said: \"Delay/postpone him and his brother and send in the villages/urban cities gatherers"
  26,37,They come to you with every knowledgeable magician/sorcerer
  26,38,So the magicians/sorcerers were gathered/collected to a known appointed place day/time
  26,39,"And (it) was said to the people: \"Are you gathering/uniting"
  26,40,"Maybe/perhaps we follow the magicians/sorcerers, if they, they were, the defeaters"
  26,41,"So when the magicians/sorcerers came, they said to Pharaoh: \"Is for us a reward/wage/fee (E) if we, we were the defeaters"
  26,42,"He said: \"Yes and you are then from (E) the neared/closer"
  26,43,"Moses said to them: \"Throw/throw away what you are throwing/throwing away"
  26,44,"So they threw/threw away their ropes/ties and their sticks/canes, and they said: \"With Pharaoh`s glory/might ,that we, we are the defeaters"
  26,45,"So Moses threw/threw away his stick/cane, so then it snatches/swallows quickly what they lie/falsify"
  26,46,So the magicians/sorcerers were thrown/thrown away prostrating
  26,47,"They said: \"We believed with the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,48,Moses` Lord and Aaron`s
  26,49,"He said: \"You believed to him before that I permit/allow for you, that he truly is your greatest/teacher and leader (E) who taught/instructed you the magic/sorcery, so you will/shall (E) know I will cut off/sever (E) your hands and your feet from opposites (sides), and I will crucify you/place you on crosses (E) all/all together"
  26,50,"They said: \"No harm/pain , that we to our Lord are returning"
  26,51,"That we wish/hope/covet that our Lord forgives for us our sins/mistakes , that we were first (of)259the believers"
  26,52,"And We inspired/transmitted to Moses that: \"Travel/depart at night with My worshippers/slaves, that you are being followed"
  26,53,So Pharaoh sent in the cities/towns gatherers (who said)
  26,54,"That, those (are) a small group/portion (E) few/little"
  26,55,And that they truly are for us angering/enraging (E)
  26,56,And that we (E) (are) all together (E) cautious
  26,57,So We brought them out from treed gardens/paradises and water springs/wells
  26,58,And treasures/buried treasures and (an) honoured/generous position/status
  26,59,"As/like that, and We made it be inherited (to) Israel`s sons and daughters"
  26,60,So they followed them at sunrise
  26,61,"So when the two groups/gatherings saw each other, Moses` friends/company said: \"That we are being caught up/overtaken (E)"
  26,62,"He said: \"No but that truly with me (is) my Lord, He will guide me"
  26,63,"So We inspired/transmitted to Moses that: \"Beat/strike/move with your stick/cane the sea/large body of water .\" So it broke in half/split open/cracked, so every/each part/piece was as the huge mountain, the great"
  26,64,And We advanced/brought near the others/lasts there at the same time or place (We made them almost catch up)
  26,65,And We saved/rescued Moses and who (is) with him all/all together
  26,66,Then We drowned/sunk the others
  26,67,"That in that (is) an evidence/sign (E) , and most of them were not believing"
  26,68,"And that your Lord He is (E) the glorious/mighty, the merciful"
  26,69,And read/recite on (to) them Abraham`s information/news
  26,70,"When He said to his father and his nation: \"What (do) you worship"
  26,71,"They said: \"We worship idols/statues so we continue/remain to it devoting/dedicating"
  26,72,"He said: \"Do they hear/listen to you when/if you call"
  26,73,Or they benefit you or they harm
  26,74,"They said: \"But we found our fathers as/like that they make/do"
  26,75,"He said: \"Did you see/understand what you were worshipping"
  26,76,You and your fathers/forefathers the eldest/old/ancient
  26,77,So they truly are an enemy to me except the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord
  26,78,"Who created me, so He guides me"
  26,79,And who He feeds me and He gives me drink
  26,80,"And if I became sick/diseased, so He cures/heals me"
  26,81,"And who makes me die, then revives/makes me alive"
  26,82,And who I wish/hope/covet that He forgives for me my sin/wrong (on) the Judgment`s Day/Resurrection260Day
  26,83,"My Lord, grant/present for me judgment/rule and make me catch up/join with the correct/righteous"
  26,84,And make/put for me (a) truth`s tongue/speech in the ends/lasts/others
  26,85,And make/put me from the blessing`s/comfort and eases` treed garden`s/paradise`s heirs
  26,86,"And forgive to my father, that he truly was from the misguided"
  26,87,And do not shame/disgrace me (on) a day/time they are being resurrected/revived
  26,88,A day/time property/possession and nor sons/sons and daughters do not benefit
  26,89,Except who came (to) God with a sound/safe (clear) heart/mind
  26,90,And paradise was advanced/brought near to the fearing and obeying
  26,91,And the Hell/place of intense heat was made to emerge for the misguided/lured
  26,92,"And (it) was said to them: \"Where (is) what you were worshipping"
  26,93,From other than God? Do they give you victory/aid or they become victorious
  26,94,"So they were thrown down in it, they and the enticing"
  26,95,And Satan`s soldiers/warriors all/all together
  26,96,They said and (while) they are in it disputing/arguing
  26,97,"By God, that truly we were in clear/evident misguidance"
  26,98,When/if we make you equal with the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord
  26,99,And none except the criminals/sinners misguided us
  26,100,So (there are) none for us from mediators
  26,101,And nor a concerned friend
  26,102,And if that (E) (there were) for us a return/repetition so we be/become from the believers
  26,103,"That truly in that (is) an evidence/sign (E) , and most of them were not believing"
  26,104,"And that truly your Lord, He is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"
  26,105,Noah`s nation denied the messengers
  26,106,"When their brother Noah, said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,107,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,108,"So fear and obey God, and obey me"
  26,109,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,110,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,111,"They said: \"Do we believe to you, and the mean/low/despised followed you"
  26,112,"He said: \"And what is my knowledge with what they were making/doing"
  26,113,"That truly their account/calculation (is) except on my Lord, if you feel/know/sense"
  26,114,And I am not with expelling/forcing out the believers
  26,115,That I am except a clear/evident warner/giver of notice
  26,116,"They said: \"If (E) you do not end/terminate/stop, you Noah, you will be/become (E) from the stoned"
  26,117,"He said: \"My Lord, that truly my nation denied me"
  26,118,"So judge/open between me and between them (between me and them) an opening/victory, and save/rescue me and who (is) with me from the believers"
  26,119,"So We saved/rescued him and who (was) with him in the ship/ships, the full/loaded"
  26,120,Then We drowned/sunk after (that) the remainders
  26,121,"That in that (is) an evidence/sign (E) , and most of them were not believing"
  26,122,"And that truly your Lord, he is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"
  26,123,Aad denied the messengers
  26,124,"When/if their brother Hood said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,125,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,126,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,127,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universe`s) Lord"
  26,128,"Do you build/construct at every/each high hill an evidence , something useless in vanity"
  26,129,"And you take factories , maybe/perhaps you be immortal/eternal"
  26,130,"And if you destroyed/attacked violently, you destroyed/attacked violently (as) tyrants/rebels"
  26,131,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,132,And fear and obey who extended/spread you with what you know
  26,133,He extended/spread you with camels/livestock and sons/sons and daughters
  26,134,And treed gardens/paradises and water springs/wells
  26,135,That I fear on (for) you a great day`s` torture
  26,136,"They said: \"(It is) equal/alike on (to) us, had you preached/advised , or you did not be from the preachers/advisers"
  26,137,That truly that (is) except the first`s/beginner`s nature/character
  26,138,And we are not with being tortured
  26,139,"So they denied him , so We made them die/destroyed them, that truly in that (is) an evidence/sign (E), and most of them were not believing"
  26,140,"And that truly your Lord He is (E), the glorious/mighty , the merciful"
  26,141,Thamud denied the messengers
  26,142,"When/if their brother Saleh said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,143,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,144,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,145,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,146,Are you going to be left in what (is) here here safe/secure
  26,147,In treed gardens/paradises and water springs/wells
  26,148,"And plants/crops and palm trees, its first fruit of the season (is) slender/digestible (fine)"
  26,149,And you actively/cleverly carve out from the mountains houses/homes
  26,150,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,151,And do not obey the spoilers`/extravagators` order/command/matter/affair
  26,152,"Those who corrupt/disorder in the earth/Planet Earth, and they do not correct/repair"
  26,153,"They said: \"Truly/but you are from the bewitched/enchanted"
  26,154,"You are not except (a) human equal/alike to us , so come/bring with an evidence/sign/verse if you were from the truthful"
  26,155,"He said: \"This is a female camel, for it (is) a share of water/drink, and for you a known day`s/time`s share of water/drink"
  26,156,And do not touch it with harm/evil (then) a great day`s torture takes/punishes you
  26,157,"So they wounded it/slaughtered it/made it infertile, so they became/became in the morning regretful/remorseful"
  26,158,"So the torture punished/took them, that in that (is) an evidence/sign (E) , and most of them were not believing"
  26,159,"And that truly your Lord He is (E), the glorious/mighty, the merciful"
  26,160,Lot`s nation denied the messengers
  26,161,"When their brother, Lot, said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,162,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,163,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,164,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universe`s) Lord"
  26,165,Do you come/commit (sexually to) the males from the creations all together/(universes)
  26,166,"And you leave what your Lord created for you from your wives/spouses , but/rather, you are a nation transgressing/violating"
  26,167,"They said: \"If (E) you do not end/terminate/stop, you Lot, you will be/become (E) from the brought/driven out"
  26,168,"He said: \"That I am to your deed from the hating"
  26,169,My Lord save/rescue me and my family/people from what they make/do
  26,170,So We saved/rescued him and his family/people all/all together
  26,171,Except old/weak (F) (was) in the remaining behind
  26,172,Then We destroyed the others
  26,173,"And We rained on them rain, so it became bad/harmful , the warned`s/given notice`s rain"
  26,174,"That in that (is) an evidence/sign/verse (E), and most of them were not believing"
  26,175,"And that your Lord, He is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"
  26,176,The thicket`s/dense tangled trees` owners/friends/company denied the messengers
  26,177,"When/if Shu`aib said to them: \"Do you not fear and obey"
  26,178,That I am for you a faithful messenger
  26,179,So fear and obey God and obey me
  26,180,"And I do not ask/beg you on it from a wage/fee/reward, that truly my wage/reward (is) except on the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord"
  26,181,"Fulfill/complete the measurement/weight, and do not be from the reducers/decreasers (cheaters)"
  26,182,And weigh/measure with the scale/measure the balanced
  26,183,"And do not reduce/cheat the people (of) their things, and do not corrupt in the earth/Planet Earth corrupting/disordering"
  26,184,"And fear and obey who created you, and the nation/creation, the first/beginners"
  26,185,"They said: \"Truly/indeed you are from the bewitched/enchanted"
  26,186,"And you are not except (a) human similar/equal to us , and that truly we suspect you (are) from (E) the liars/falsifiers"
  26,187,So drop on us pieces from the sky/space if you were from the truthful
  26,188,"He said: \"My Lord (is) more knowledgeable with (about) what you make/do"
  26,189,"So they denied him , so torture (of) the shade`s day/time punished/took them, that it truly was a great day`s/time`s torture"
  26,190,That in that (is) an evidence/sign/verse (E) and most of them were not believing
  26,191,"And that your Lord He is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"
  26,192,And that it truly is descent (E) (from) Lord (of) the creations all together/(universes)
  26,193,"The Soul/Spirit , the faithful/loyal , descended with it"
  26,194,On your heart/mind to be (E) from the warners/givers of notice
  26,195,With a clear/evident Arabic tongue/language/speech
  26,196,And that it truly is in (E) the first`s/beginner`s Books
  26,197,"Was not an evidence/sign/verse (to) be for them, that Israel`s sons` and daughters` learned ones/knowledgeable know it? (Was not an evidence for them that the Israelites` scholars know of it)"
  26,198,And even if We descended it on (to) some (of) the non-Arabs/Persians
  26,199,"So he read it on (to) them, (and) they were not with it believing"
  26,200,As/like that We entered it in the criminals`/sinners` hearts/minds
  26,201,"They do not believe with it until they see the torture, the painful"
  26,202,"So it comes to them suddenly/unexpectedly, and (while) they are not feeling/knowing/sensing"
  26,203,"So they say: \"Are we delayed"
  26,204,Are (they) with Our torture hastening/urging
  26,205,So did you see if We gave them long life/made them enjoy years
  26,206,Then came to them what they were being promised
  26,207,What they were being made to enjoy did not enrich/suffice (benefit) from them
  26,208,"And We did not destroy from a village/urban city, except for it (are) warners/givers of notice"
  26,209,"A remembrance/reminder, and We were not unjust/oppressive"
  26,210,And the devils did not descend with it
  26,211,"And (it) should not (be) for them, and they are not able"
  26,212,"That they truly are from the hearing/listening , they are being separated/isolated (E)"
  26,213,"So do not call with God another god, so you be/become from the tortured ones"
  26,214,And warn/give notice (to) your father`s near relations/tribe the nearest/closest
  26,215,And be lenient/comforting your wing/side (be kind) to who followed you from the believers
  26,216,"So if they disobeyed you, so say: \"That I am innocent/renouncing from what you make/do"
  26,217,"And rely/depend on the glorious/mighty, the merciful"
  26,218,Who sees you when you stand/get up
  26,219,And your turning in (between) the prostrating
  26,220,"That He truly is the hearing/listening, the knowledgeable"
  26,221,"Do I inform you, on (to) whom the devils descend"
  26,222,"(They) descend on (to) every/each liar/falsifier, sinner/criminal"
  26,223,"They listen attentively the hearing/listening , and most of them (are) lying/denying"
  26,224,"And the poets, (only) the misguiding/failing follow them"
  26,225,Do you not see that they truly are in every/each valley they wander about confused
  26,226,And that they truly say what they do not make/do
  26,227,"Except those who believed and made/did the correct/righteous deeds and they remembered/mentioned God much, and they became victorious from after what they were caused injustice to/oppressed ; and those who caused injustice/oppressed will know which place of return , they return to"
  27,1,"T S , those are the Koran`s verses/evidences , and a clear/evident Book"
  27,2,Guidance and good news to the believers
  27,3,"Those who keep up the prayers and give/bring the charity/purification , and they are with the end (other life), they are sure/certain"
  27,4,"That those who do not believe with the end (other life), We decorated/beautified for them their deeds , so they are being confused/puzzled"
  27,5,"Those are for them the torture`s harm/evil , and they are in the end (other life), they are the most losers"
  27,6,"And that you are made to receive/meet/find (E) the Koran from at (a) wise/judicious, knowledgeable"
  27,7,"When/if Moses said to his family/relation : \"That I, I perceived/saw a fire, I will come to you from it with a news/information , or I come to you with a flame flame/torch , maybe/perhaps you warm (yourselves)"
  27,8,"So when he came to it, (it) was called: \"That is/was blessed who is in the fire/mark and who (is) around/surrounding it, and God`s praise/glory (is) to the nations all together`s/(universe`s) Lord"
  27,9,"You Moses, that it truly is I, God, the glorious/mighty , the wise/judicious"
  27,10,"And throw/throw away your stick/cane, so when he saw it , it shakes/moves as if it is a Jinn he turned away giving his back, and he did not follow/succeed/track: \"You Moses, do not fear, that I, the messengers do not fear at/by/near Me"
  27,11,"Except who caused injustice/oppression then exchanged/replaced good after bad/evil/harm, so I am forgiving, merciful"
  27,12,"And enter your hand in your collar/opening it appears/emerges white from without bad/evil/harm, in nine evidences/signs to Pharaoh and his nation, that they truly were a nation (of) debauchers"
  27,13,"So when Our signs/evidences came to them manifest/clearly visible to the eye and understanding, they said: \"That (is) clear/evident magic/sorcery"
  27,14,"And they disbelieved and denied with it, and their selves became sure/certain of it, unjustly/oppressively and height, might and dignity, so look/see how was the corruptings` end/turn (result)"
  27,15,"And We had (E) given David and Soliman knowledge, and they (B) said: \"The praise/gratitude (is) to God who preferred/favoured us over many from His slaves/worshippers , the believers"
  27,16,"And Soliman inherited David, and he said: \"You, you the people we had been taught the birds` speech (language)/logic, and we were given from every thing, that truly that it is (E) the grace/favour/blessing , the clear/evident"
  27,17,"And was gathered for Soliman his soldiers/warriors from the Jinns and the human/mankind, and the birds, so they are being restrained/apportioned (mobilized)"
  27,18,"Until when they passed by the ants` valley, an ant said: \"You, you the ants, enter your residences, (let) not Soliman and his warriors smash/destroy you (E) and they are not feeling/sensing"
  27,19,"So he smiled laughing/wondering from its saying/word, and he said: \"My Lord, inspire/influence me that I thank/be grateful (for) your blessing which you blessed on me and on my parents, and that I make/do correct/righteous deeds You accept/approve it, and enter me with Your mercy in (between) Your worshippers/slaves the correct/righteous"
  27,20,"And he seeked/searched the bird/birds , so he said: \"Why (it is) not for me, I do not see the hoopoe bird/clucking bird , or he was from the absent? I will torture him strong (severe) torture"
  27,21,"I will slaughter it (E) , or it comes/brings to me (E) with a proof/evidence clear/evident"
  27,22,"So it waited/remained not far/distant, so it said: \"I became aware/enveloped with what you did not become aware (of)/envelope with it, and I came to you from Sheba with sure/certain news/information"
  27,23,"That I found a woman, she owns/rules them, and she was given from every thing, and for her (is) a great throne"
  27,24,"I found her and her nation prostrating to the sun, from other than God, and the devil decorated/beautified for them their deeds , so he prevented/obstructed them from the way/path , so they do not be guided"
  27,25,"Do they not prostrate to God who brings out the hidden/concealed in the skies/space and the earth/Planet Earth, and he knows what you hide, and what you declare/publicize"
  27,26,"God, no God except Him, Lord (of) the throne , the great"
  27,27,"He said: \"We will look/see , had you been truthful, or you were from the liars/falsifiers"
  27,28,"Go/take away , with my Book/letter/message, this, so throw it to them, then turn away from them, so look/see what they return"
  27,29,"She said: \"You, you the nobles/assembly , that I , was/is thrown to me (an) honoured/generous Book"
  27,30,"That it truly is from Soliman, and that it truly is by God`s name the merciful, the most merciful"
  27,31,"That do not become high, mighty and dignified over me, and come to me (as) Moslems/submitters"
  27,32,"She said: \"You, you the nobles/assembly , give me your opinion in my matter/affair/order/command, I was not deciding a matter/affair/order/command until you witness/testify"
  27,33,"They said: \"We are (owners) of power/strength, and (owners) of strong (severe) courage/might/power, and the matter/affair/order/command (is) to you, so think about what you order/command"
  27,34,"She said: \"That truly the kings if they entered a village/urban city they corrupted it and they made/put its more dignified/honoured people , humiliated/disgraced , and as/like that they make/do"
  27,35,"And that I am sending to them with a present, so (then I am) looking/considering with what the messengers return"
  27,36,"So when (he) came (to) Soliman, he said: \"Do you extend/spread me with property/wealth ? So what God gave me, (is) better than what He gave you, but you with your present, you be happy"
